SIMPLE: bicentennial
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Bicentennial
<hw>Bi`cen*ten"ni*al</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>bi-</ets> +
<ets>centennial</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting of two hundred
years.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Occurring every two hundred years.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bicentennial</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bicentennial
<hw>Bi`cen*ten"ni*al</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The two hundredth year or
anniversary, or its celebration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bicephalous</ent>⟦br⟧
